caller_intent: Tracy Southern wants to make a payment on her insurance policy.
resolution_steps: Agent logs into National General system to access Tracy's policy details.
Agent confirms policy address (1115 Okaloosa Drive) and payment amount ($63.55).
Agent processes payment using credit card ending in 0186.
Agent sends payment confirmation via email and provides confirmation number (20573535).
knowledge_required: Accessing and navigating National General carrier portal
summary: Tracy Southern contacted Alliance Insurance to make a policy payment. The agent accessed National General, verified policy details, processed the payment via credit card, and sent confirmation via email. The call concluded with Tracy writing down the confirmation number.
